transcript.text: Hello everyone, we are happy to present new Photo Print module.
Photo Print module is an addition to On Print shop exclusive specialized designer studios to offer personalized experience and multi print product segment.

On Pin Shop offers integrated web to print and print order management solution with five specialized designer studios like Photo print module, canvas module, Commercial white format, Promotional studio, Photo book studio and calendar and diary studio.
Each of these designer studios are developed to offer high end and personal experience to end client while designing specific products in your online storefront.
The global photo print market is expected to grow at CAGR of 12.3% by 2023.
You can capture the fastest growing market by offering photo printing online to your end clients in your existing on prints of storefront.
With photo print model, your clients can easily print their photos and trace of their memories with family and friends.
So let me take you through customer journey for Photo print model.
Photo print model is developed keeping in mind with entity units and quick ordering for multiple photos and offer best experience to end clients while ordering photo prints in your online storefront.
Here they can upload and select multiple pictures which they would like to print and order on your website.
Client can select pictures from PC, laptop or mobile.
It is also ready with the social media and cloud API so they can also use images from Facebook, Instagram or from Google Drive or a Dropbox.
The challenge offering photo print is giving flexibility to client to order multiple pictures and ordering different size and options.
So here in photo builder screen they're able to see all the pictures and for each picture they're able to change the size, quantity and the finishing options from a single screen for each picture.
They're also able to see the image quality as per the DPI settings.
We are done so they can see that image is a high quality, low quality or a medium quality on the photo builder screen.
Also they can add it in picture.
In the added picture they have an option to adjust the image, change the orientation, rotate the image, even apply the border in different colors and flip the image.
Also here 2 very intelligent options are given to end client.
Apply all means if end client wants to have all images or all same size images in same specification or the same quantity they can apply all and it will apply all the options in all the images.
It says lot of time for end client as they don't have to go in each image and select the similar finishing options or quantity.
Also there is another option called add another size.
Here N client can order their favorite pictures in other sizes with simple click.
They don't have to upload the same image again and select other size.
Now after applying all settings they can order all these photo prints easily.
And now with the checkout they can also see the summary of all pictures sizes and quantity.
They can see number of images they are ordered in each size as well as in the finishing options.
So in three simple steps and in matter of minutes, your end clients can order photo prints on your website.
Hope you like the photo print module.
Please visit on Pin shop.com or contact us for personalized demo.
